### 标准化元数据模板

所有文章的元数据都应该遵循以下格式：

- **元数据模板**：`METADATA_TEMPLATE.json`
- **关键字段**：title, author, publishTime, tags, category, priority, wordCount, codeSnippets, readingTime, difficulty, estimatedMetrics, keywords, summary, contentStructure, targetAudience, valueProposition, callToAction, publishPlan, references, type, status

